  <para><emphasis role="bold">Description:</emphasis></para>

  <para>This CGI allows you to view objects (i.e. hosts, host groups, contacts, contact groups, time periods, services, etc.) that you have
  defined in your <link xlink:href="configobject">object configuration file(s)</link>.</para>

  <para><emphasis role="bold">Authorization Requirements:</emphasis></para>

  <itemizedlist>
    <listitem>
      <para>You must be <link xlink:href="configcgi#authorized_for_configuration_information"> <emphasis>authorized for configuration
      information</emphasis> </link> in order to any kind of configuration information.</para>
    </listitem>
  </itemizedlist>

