  <para><emphasis role="bold">Description:</emphasis></para>

  <para>This CGI is used to display host and service notifications that have been sent to various contacts. The output is basically a subset
  of the information that is displayed by the <link linkend="cgis-showlog_cgi">log file CGI</link>. You have the ability to filter the
