  sent to specific contacts, etc). If you have <link xlink:href="configmain#log_rotation_method">log rotation</link> enabled, you can browse
  notifications present in archived log files by using the navigational links near the top of the page.</para>

  <para><emphasis role="bold">Authorization Requirements:</emphasis></para>

